summary: My current character, i\'m uplading her on Nexus because I\'m pretty satisfied by the final result and wanted to share it.
descriptionHtml:
Freyja Brightwinter is a Nord from wherever you want ;)

I tried to make her as realistic as possible by avoiding to give her a too much beautiful face. The main goal was before all to do a lore-friendly character.



[b]Mods Used [/b]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666//?]Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE-[/url] [i][b]by Caliente[/b][/i]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6554//?]CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible[/url] [i][b]by navetsea[/b][/i]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29791/?]No More Ugly Bronze Shine[/url] [i][b]by COTS[/b][/i]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4502//?]Better Freckles[/url] [i][b]by MadCat221[/b][/i]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5701//?]RANs Eyeliner Replacer[/url] [i][b]by RAN46[/b][/i]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair[/url] [i][b]by Apachii[/b][/i]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4869/?]Covereyes[/url] [i][b]by mrLenski[/b][/i]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26354//?]LiFE - Lith Face Enhancement -CBBE-UNP-UNPB[/url] [i][b]by LithiumFlower[/b][/i] ( VERY recommended )


The save has been done with a French version of the game, but there shouldn\'t be any problems about that.

You will start with Hadvar in the Helgen Keep.


Have fun, and please endorse if you like her :)
author: Willv091 aka Kilmaat
